@adrianl7147  @adrianl7147  Smugness and arrogance are ideal prerequisites to getting burned. If not financially, then emotionally. 
Would you mind pointing out the part in my comment where I said I think everyone is honest and that you should trust blindly? You completely missed my point.
Btw, I've never gotten scammed to date--au contraire. You could say that due to my work in the legal/LE fields, I have a heightened awareness. But I also know how sophisticated fraudsters can be, and that NO ONE is completely safe from falling victim to one scam or another.
